              Instagram
            </p>
            <iframe
              src="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DWFYQpsjyZX/embed/"
              width="280"
              height="500"
              frameborder="0"
              scrolling="no"
              allowtransparency="true"
              loading="lazy"
              title="Reel Instagram — IME Calibraciones"
            ></iframe>
          </div>

          <div class="nosotros-redes__embed-wrap">
            <p class="nosotros-redes__embed-label">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" width="14" height="14"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 00-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 00.502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 002.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 002.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
